Multi-Arch: foreign
Description: CIX GPU driver DKMS package
 This package provides DKMS source for the CIX GPU kernel modules used on
 CIX platforms.
 .
 DKMS rebuilds the modules for the installed kernel when matching kernel
 headers are available on the target system.
